OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA few showers possible today
OL,6,Fover Tayside and Angus, but for most
OL,7,Fit will remain dry with bright and
OL,8,Fsunny spells breaking through the
OL,9,Fcloud. Mostly light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will be a dry evening with
OL,12,Flate sunny spells leading to clear
OL,13,Fspells after sunset. Overnight
OL,14,Fremaining dry with any cloud clearing
OL,15,Fto give clear skies. Light winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FA dry morning with bright
OL,18,Fand sunny spells. Turning cloudier
OL,19,Fthrough the afternoon with light rain
OL,20,Fspreading eastwards through the
OL,21,Fafternoon and evening. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
