OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy with heavy showers on Sunday.
OL,7,FDrier on Monday with sunny spells, the
OL,8,Fodd shower possible. Strong winds at
OL,9,Ftimes on Tuesday with rain clearing to
OL,10,Fheavy showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
